      "role": "user",
      "content": "got it. so once those melanoidins start forming, does the reaction just keep going until the bread is burnt, or is there a point where it stabilizes? and is there any way to control the speed of those \"intermediate\" reactions to get more flavor without losing control of the temp?",
      "source": "evaluator"
